data.text: @TheSiouxzy I was hoping R would have thought to bring you guys!!! But I agree with you completely.

@MissEEG I don’t know anyone here but J & R. 😄 R got his. J doesn’t qualify either. It’s ok. I just need to be patient. The way I see it, I safely traveled & saw people last year & was fine so what are a few more months of waiting.

@TheSiouxzy You may try going with someone who does qualify. I’ve heard from 3 friends they went with & got vaccinated too. Idk why or how...maybe people no showed so they don’t want to waste. I’m trying this too
